          "href": "https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/web-app-manifest/",
          "target": "_blank"
        },
        "Web Manifest"
      ],
      ". While it's possible to add both of these to an app manually, a base project from Create React App (CRA) and the Ionic CLI provides this already."
    ],
    " ",
